description: When you two were younger, she gave you some advice about dealing with suicide - 'Everyone thinks about it, but it's only the dumbasses who actually do it'. Then she went on to work in a morgue, and fuck your best friend. They got married, their lives imploded, and your friend drank himself to death. It may be that the arc of badass to hollow is more severe than we anticipate.
name: Ventricular Oblique
